summary: This is a modified Kubikiribocho that uses the Ax animations, and can be Crafted and upgraded
descriptionHtml:
This is a modified Kubikiribocho that uses the Ax animations, and can be Crafted and upgraded. You can find it under Daedric in the forge and at the sharpening stone. It currently does not require a skill in order to craft.

This mod has been given permission to be updated by Cha0sr1pper from the origional Author.You must contact Urwy and obtain his permission before re-packaging any part of this mod. If He does not respond within 2 weeks, you are free to use it as you see fit, on the condition that you do give credit where it is due.
His original mod can be found at http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=11874
author: Cha0sr1pper
